Algorithm:
Start
Input: Read the integer value of n (upper limit).
Initialize: Set sum = 0.
Loop: Iterate from i = 1 to n:
If i is an even number (i.e., i % 2 == 0), add i to sum.
Output: Display the value of sum.
End

Pseudocode:
Start
    Input n
    Set sum = 0
    For i from 1 to n do
        If i % 2 == 0 then
            sum = sum + i
        End If
    End For
    Output sum
End